"n.虚假 【考】 反义词：truthfulnes s(真实) n. 虚假; 撒谎癖 【反】truthfulness(n 真实; 坦率); candor(n 坦白; 直率); honesty(n 诚实; 正直); veracity(n 说真实话) 【记】mend 不断修改的,说真话不用辩解, 说假话总需修改以前的话 mendacity (n.)  ""tendency to lie,"" 1640s, from Middle French mendacité and directly from Late Latin mendacitas ""falsehood, mendacity,"" from Latin mendax ""lying; a liar"" (see mendacious)."
